text: Very yummy prata and thosai. Take away but still fresh and good. Delicious and generous portion of curries given! Curries all thick and not diluted. Will definitely come back again.

It's in the residential district of Bedok Reservoir in Singapore. The food are marvelous, it's a different kind of taste that you can never get in Malaysia. If you in Singapore, try coming to this restaurant. Recommended.
